co-op. If you're going to be stuck in hell, it may as well be with your friends!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157130/extras/4b01ea8de47ec624165ff032479ed0cb.poster.avif?t=1667325239\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157130/extras/4b01ea8de47ec624165ff032479ed0cb.webm?t=1667325239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157130/extras/4b01ea8de47ec624165ff032479ed0cb.mp4?t=1667325239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>See you in the abyss!",
